<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About - Suprizly</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/about.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>
  <main>
    <div class="about">
      <h1>Bringing Joy To Your Door Step!</h1>
      <p>We believe life's best moments come from unexpected surprises. That's why we've made it our mission to curate mystery boxes that spark joy and genuine excitement.</p>
      <h3>#OurStory</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="mission">
      <div class="discription">
        <h1>Our Mission</h1>
        <p>In world of the predictable shopping experinces, we are bringing back the magic of surprise. Rvery box we create is thoughtfully curated to introduce you to new products, brands and experiences you might have not experirnced in this world.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="icons">
        <div class="heart">
          <i class="fa fa-heart"></i>
          <p>Made With Love</p>
        </div>
        <div class="star">
          <i class="far fa-star"></i>
          <p>Curated Surprizes</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="numbers">
        <h1>By The Numbers </h1>
        <div class="Delivered">
          <h2>50,000+</h2>
          <p>Boxes Delivered</p>
        </div>
        <div class="Customers">
          <h2>15,000+</h2>
          <p>Happy Customers</p>
        </div>
        <div class="Served">
          <h2>25+</h2>
          <p>Countries Served</p>
        </div>
        <div class="Reviews">
          <h2>98%</h2>
          <p>5-Star Reviews</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="team">
        <h1>Meet The DREAM Team </h1>
        <div class="member1">
          <h3>Nakshtr Gupta</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="member2">
          <h3>Ananshi Sharma</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="member2">
          <h3>Arpit Singal</h3>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="join-club">
      <h2>Join the <span>Surprise Club</span></h2>
      <p>Get exclusive access to limited boxes and special member discounts.</p>
      <div class="subscribe-form">
        <input id="emailInput" type="email" placeholder="Enter your email...">
        <button id="subscribeBtn">Subscribe</button>
      </div>
      <div id="messageArea"></div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  <script src="/js/about.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
